{"title_page": "See the Light (The Jeff Healey Band album)", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = See the Light\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[The Jeff Healey Band]]\n| cover      = See the Light album cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = September 13, 1988\n| recorded   = 1988\n| venue      =\n| studio     = The Complex, Los Angeles\n| genre      = [[Blues rock]]\n| length     = 48:52\n| label      = [[Arista Records|Arista]]\n| producer   = [[Jimmy Iovine]], [[Greg Ladanyi]], [[Thom Panunzio]]\n| prev_title =\n| prev_year  =\n| next_title = [[Hell to Pay (Jeff Healey album)|Hell to Pay]]\n| next_year  = 1990\n}}\n\n{{Album ratings\n| rev1 = [[AllMusic]]\n| rev1Score = {{Rating|4|5}} <ref>{{Allmusic |class=album |id=r9115 |tab=review |label=The Jeff Healey Band: ''See the Light'' > Review |first=Thom |last=Owens |accessdate=29 June 2011}}</ref>\n|rev2 = ''[[Encyclopedia of Popular Music]]''\n|rev2Score = {{Rating|4|5}}<ref>{{cite book|last=Larkin|first=Colin|authorlink=Colin Larkin|title=Encyclopedia of Popular Music|year=2007|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]]|edition=4th|isbn=978-0195313734|title-link=Encyclopedia of Popular Music}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''''See the Light''''' is the debut album by [[the Jeff Healey Band]]. It was released on September 13, 1988. It was No. 50 of the top 100 albums in Canada in 1989.<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.6625&type=1 |title=Top 100 Albums of '89 |date={{date|December 23, 1989}} |magazine=RPM |issue=Volume 51, No. 8 |publisher=archived at [[Library and Archives Canada]] |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024090643/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.6625&type=1 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |url-status=dead }}</ref> In 1990 it was nominated for an \"[[Juno Award for Album of the Year#Album of the Year (1980\u20131998)|Album of the Year]]\" [[Juno Award]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://junoawards.ca/database/artist-summary/?artist_name=The+Jeff+Healey+Band |title=Artist Summary: The Jeff Healey Band |publisher=junoawards.ca |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}} }}{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{tracklist\n| title1   = Confidence Man\n| writer1  = [[John Hiatt]]\n| length1  = 3:12\n| title2   = My Little Girl\n| writer2  = [[Jeff Healey]]\n| length2  = 3:10\n| title3   = River of No Return\n| writer3  = [[Keith Reid]], [[Jon Tiven]], [[Sally Tiven]]\n| length3  = 3:31\n| title4   = Don't Let Your Chance Go By\n| writer4  = Healey\n| length4  = 3:20\n| title5   = [[Angel Eyes (Jeff Healey song)|Angel Eyes]]\n| writer5  = Hiatt, [[Fred Koller]]\n| length5  = 5:19\n| title6   = Nice Problem to Have\n| writer6  = [[Robbie Blunt]], Jeff Healey, Joe Rockman, Tom Stephen\n| length6  = 4:50\n| title7   = Someday, Someway\n| writer7  = [[Martin Briley]], [[Danny Tate]]\n| length7  = 3:28\n| title8   = I Need to Be Loved\n| writer8  = Healey\n| length8  = 3:43\n| title9   = Blue Jean Blues\n| writer9  = [[Frank Beard (musician)|Frank Beard]], [[Billy Gibbons]], [[Dusty Hill]]\n| length9  = 5:39\n| title10  = That's What They Say\n| writer10 = Healey\n| length10 = 4:27\n| title11  = Hideaway\n| writer11 = [[Freddie King]], [[Sonny Thompson]]\n| length11 = 4:26\n| title12  = See the Light\n| writer12 = Healey\n| length12 = 4:26\n}}\n\n==Production==\n*Produced By Jimmy Iovine, Greg Ladanyi & Thom Panunzio\n*Assistant Producer: Debbie Sommer\n*Mixed & Engineered By Greg Ladanyi & Thom Panunzio\n*Additional Engineering By Duane Seykora & Sharon Rice\n*Mastered By Ron Lewter & [[Doug Sax]]\n\n==Personnel==\n*[[Jeff Healey]]: Guitars, Harmonica, Lead Vocals\n*Joe Rockman: Bass, Backing Vocals\n*Tom Stephen: Drums, Percussion\n*[[Robbie Blunt]]: Guitars\n*[[Bobbye Hall]]: Percussion\n*Kipp Lennon, Mark Lennon, Michael Lennon, Pat Lennon, [[Marilyn Martin]], [[Timothy B. Schmit]]: Additional Backing Vocals \n*[[Benmont Tench]]: Keyboards\n\n==Chart positions==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! style=\"vertical-align:bottom\" class=\"unsortable\"| Year \n! style=\"vertical-align:bottom\" class=\"unsortable\"| Chart \n! style=\"vertical-align:bottom\"| Peak<br />Position\n|-\n| 1989\n| US [[Billboard 200|''Billboard'' 200]]<ref>{{Allmusic |class=album |id=r9115 |tab=charts-awards |label=\"''See the Light'' > Charts & Awards > Billboard Albums\" |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 22\n|-\n| 1989\n| Canadian [[RPM (magazine)|RPM]] 100<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.6424&type=1 |title=RPM 100 Albums |date={{date|August 07 1989}} |magazine=RPM |volume=50|number=15 |via=Library and Archives Canada |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024090702/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.6424&type=1 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 25\n|-\n| 1989\n| [[UK Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Jeff Healey Band: See the Light |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/search/albums/See%20The%20Light |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}} |df= }}</ref> \n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 58 \n|-\n| 1989\n| NZ [[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand|RIANZ]] Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=https://charts.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&titel=See+The+Light&cat=a |title=The Jeff Healey Band - See the Light |publisher=charts.nz |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 17 \n|-\n| 1989\n| Australian [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]] Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&titel=See+The+Light&cat=a |title=The Jeff Healey Band - See the Light |publisher=australian-charts.com |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 33 \n|-\n| 1989\n| [[Sverigetopplistan|Swedish Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&titel=See+The+Light&cat=a |title=The Jeff Healey Band - See the Light |publisher=swedishcharts.com |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 32 \n|-\n| 1989\n| Dutch [[MegaCharts#Mega Album Top 100|Mega Album Top 100]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&titel=See+The+Light&cat=a |language=Dutch |title=The Jeff Healey Band - See the Light |publisher=dutchcharts.nl |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 23 \n|-\n| 1989\n| [[Media Control Charts|German Albums Charts]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.de/album.asp?artist=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&title=See+The+Light&country=de |language=German |title=The Jeff Healey Band, See the Light |publisher=charts.de |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 33 \n|-\n| 1989\n| [[Swiss Music Charts|Swiss Albums Charts]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hitparade.ch/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Jeff+Healey+Band&titel=See+The+Light&cat=a |language=German |title=The Jeff Healey Band - See the Light |publisher=hitparade.ch |accessdate={{date|2011-09-19}}}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center\" | 13 \n|}\n\n==Certifications==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n! Country\n!align=\"center\"|Certification\n!align=\"center\"|Sales\n|-\n| Canada ([[Music Canada]])\n|align=\"center\"|3 \u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musiccanada.com/GPSearchResult.aspx?st=See%20the%20Light&ica=False&sa=The%20Jeff%20Healey%20Band&sl=&smt=0&sat=-1&ssb=Certification%20Level&ssdir=descending|title=Gold Platinum Database : ''See the Light'' : Jeff Healey Band|publisher=[[Music Canada]]|accessdate={{date|2011-09-02}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120607123415/http://www.musiccanad