 June 2012|work=cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk|publisher=Chris Turner's Snooker Archive|accessdate=26 February 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ranking History|url=http://www.snooker.org/rnk/history.asp?sort=1986/1987&order=asc|publisher=Snooker.org|accessdate=6 February 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Hayton|first=Eric|title=The CueSport Book of Professional Snooker|year=2004|publisher=Rose Villa Publications|location=Lowestoft|isbn=0-9548549-0-X|pages=119\u2013123}}</ref><ref name=cuetracker>{{cite web|title=1986/1987 Ranking List|url=http://www.cuetracker.net/pages/rankings.php?list=1986/1987&sort=start|publisher=CueTracker \u2013 Snooker Database|accessdate=4 May 2014}}</ref>\n! align=\"left\" | Name\n! align=\"left\" | Nationality\n|-\n| 1\n| [[Steve Davis]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 2\n| [[Cliff Thorburn]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 3\n| [[Dennis Taylor]]\n| {{flag|Northern Ireland}}\n|-\n| 4\n| [[Tony Knowles (snooker player)|Tony Knowles]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 5\n| [[Jimmy White]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 6\n| [[Alex Higgins]]\n| {{flag|Northern Ireland}}\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Willie Thorne]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 8\n| [[Joe Johnson (snooker player)|Joe Johnson]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Kirk Stevens]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Terry Griffiths]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 11\n| [[Tony Meo]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 12\n| [[Silvino Francisco]]\n| {{flag|South Africa|1982}}\n|-\n| 13\n| [[Neal Foulds]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 14\n| [[Doug Mountjoy]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 15\n| [[Ray Reardon]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 16\n| [[Rex Williams]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 17\n| [[John Parrott]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 18\n| [[John Campbell (snooker player)|John Campbell]]\n| {{flag|Australia}}\n|-\n| 19\n| [[John Virgo]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 20\n| [[Eugene Hughes (snooker player)|Eugene Hughes]]\n| {{flag|Ireland}}\n|-\n| 21\n| [[David Taylor (snooker player)|David Taylor]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 22\n| [[Murdo MacLeod (snooker player)|Murdo MacLeod]]\n| {{flag|Scotland}}\n|-\n| 23\n| [[Cliff Wilson]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 24\n| [[Bill Werbeniuk]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 25\n| [[Eddie Charlton]]\n| {{flag|Australia}}\n|-\n| 26\n| [[Peter Francisco (snooker player)|Peter Francisco]]\n| {{flag|South Africa|1982}}\n|-\n| 27\n| [[Mike Hallett]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 28\n| [[Dave Martin (snooker player)|Dave Martin]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 29\n| [[Dean Reynolds]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 30\n| [[Barry West]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 31\n| [[Steve Longworth]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 32\n| [[Jim Wych]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 33\n| [[Danny Fowler]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 34\n| [[John Spencer (snooker player)|John Spencer]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 35\n| [[Steve Duggan]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 36\n| [[Perrie Mans]]\n| {{flag|South Africa|1982}}\n|-\n| 37\n| [[Tony Drago]]\n| {{flag|Malta}}\n|-\n| 38\n| [[Marcel Gauvreau]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 39\n| [[Dene O'Kane]]\n| {{flag|New Zealand}}\n|-\n| 40\n| [[Steve Newbury]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 41\n| [[Warren King (snooker player)|Warren King]]\n| {{flag|Australia}}\n|-\n| 42\n| [[Patsy Fagan]]\n| {{flag|Ireland}}\n|-\n| 43\n| [[Mark Wildman]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 44\n| [[George Scott (snooker player)|George Scott]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 45\n| [[Bob Harris (snooker player)|Bob Harris]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 46\n| [[Ray Edmonds]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 47\n| [[Fred Davis (snooker player)|Fred Davis]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 48\n| [[Paddy Browne]]\n| {{flag|Republic of Ireland}}\n|-\n| 49\n| [[Tony Chappel]]\n| {{flag|Wales}}\n|-\n| 50\n| [[Graham Cripsey]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 51\n| [[Stephen Hendry]]\n| {{flag|Scotland}}\n|-\n| 52\n| [[Graham Miles]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 53\n| [[Bob Chaperon]]\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n| 54\n| [[Malcolm Bradley]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 55\n| [[Tony Jones (snooker player)|Tony Jones]]\n| {{flag|England}}\n|-\n| 56\n| [[Wayne Jones (snooker pla